('2019-09-13 12:40:58', '2019-09-13 12:40:58', 1486, 6814, '2019-09-13 12:40:58', 64, '&lt;p&gt;Dear Veritas Customer,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are pleased to announce a new release of a Veritas product you have, you can find the specific product within the subject line. As a customer with current maintenance/support on a previous version of this product, you have the added benefit of upgrading your supported licenses to this new release free of charge.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To take advantage of the latest version update please follow these simple instructions: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you are upgrading from Backup Exec 2014, 15 or 16&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Log into the Veritas Entitlement Management System by going to &lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/support\"&gt;support.veritas.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sign in and click &lt;strong&gt;Licensing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on &lt;strong&gt;Entitlements &lt;/strong&gt;(within Veritas Entitlement Management System main menu)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Expand filters by clicking &lt;strong&gt;More Options&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set the &lt;strong&gt;Product Line&lt;/strong&gt; filter to your corresponding product and click &lt;strong&gt;Apply Filters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Look for entitlements referencing the version matching the release noted in the subject line&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;To access your new software and license key(s) utilize the &lt;strong&gt;Download Software&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Generate License&lt;/strong&gt; buttons located in the Actions column&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you are updating Backup Exec 20.x&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Go to Technical Article &lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/support/en_US/article.100043577\"&gt;100043577&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Download the ZIP file attachment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Run the EXE contained in the ZIP file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;Or&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Download the ZIP file from the Veritas Entitlement Management System by following the directions provided above for upgrading from previous versions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Veritas� Backup Exec 20.5 offers Support for new Amazon S3 cloud storage tiers �Glacier, Glacier Deep Archive, Intelligent Tiering, One Zone-Infrequent Access&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Backup Exec 20.x and 16 are affected by the following issue: &lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/support/en_US/article.100045500.html\"&gt;https://www.veritas.com/support/en_US/article.100045500.html&lt;/a&gt;.  This issue has been addressed in Backup Exec 20.5.  Please refer to Article 100045500 for more information.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information on this new release, see the Version Upgrades section in the Veritas Entitlement Management System Online Help. Please remember, you are only authorized to use this release to update software copies with a current maintenance/support agreement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions, please contact your reseller or reach out to &lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/content/support/en_US/contact-us.html\"&gt;Veritas Customer Care&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Veritas Technologies, LLC&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please do not reply to this message as this email box is not monitored.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For more information regarding technical services, please refer to the &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/content/dam/Veritas/docs/policies/ga_ent_ds_Veritas_Technical_Support_Policy_en.pdf\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Veritas Support Policy&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; and other &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/content/support/en_US/terms/support-fundamentals.html\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Support Fundamentals&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; or contact your Veritas Account Manager. Visit our &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=\"https://www.veritas.com/content/support/en_US.html\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Technical Support Knowledge Base&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; for product guides and technical documentation.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=\"section_TitleTools\" class=\"row flex-column-reverse flex-lg-row mb-3\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 col-lg-10\"&gt;&lt;h1 class=\"title\"&gt;&lt;span id=\"article-page-title\"&gt;Backup Exec console crashes after installing .NET Framework 4.8.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 col-lg-2 mb-2 mb-lg-0 d-flex justify-content-end\" data-exclude=\"true\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center w-nowrap\"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=\"row\"&gt;&lt;div id=\"con_Article_HeaderTimestamp\" class=\"col-12 mb-md-3 align-items-center con_Article_HeaderTimestamp\"&gt;&lt;div id=\"el_ArticleNumber\" class=\"mr-0 mr-sm-3 mr-md-3 pr-0 pr-sm-3 pr-md-3\"&gt;Article: 100045500&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"el_ModifiedDate\" class=\"mr-0 mr-sm-3 mr-md-3 pr-0 pr-sm-3 pr-md-3\"&gt;Last Published: 2019-06-28&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"el_Ratings\" class=\"mr-0 mr-sm-3 mr-md-3 pr-0 pr-sm-3 pr-md-3\"&gt;Ratings:  116 38&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=\"row\" data-exclude=\"true\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 mb-5 con_Article_HeaderTimestamp\"&gt;&lt;div id=\"el_Products\" class=\"mr-0 pr-0\"&gt;Product(s): Backup Exec&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"section_Description\" class=\"row\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 mb-5\"&gt;&lt;div id=\"data_Description\"&gt;&lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;After installing .NET Framework 4.8 on the Backup Exec media server , the Backup Exec console crashes when starting, as shown in &lt;strong&gt;Figure 1&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This issue is also observed on servers or workstations with the Backup Exec Remote Administration console installed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Figure 1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=\"https://veritastech.custhelp.com/euf/assets/images/100045500/be_net_48.png\" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;Error Message&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following error is seen in the Windows Application Event log:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Faulting application name: BackupExec.exe, version: 20.0.1188.1863, time stamp: 0x5bc0c010&lt;br /&gt;Faulting module name: KERNELBASE.dll, version: 6.3.9600.19269, time stamp: 0x5c5e079f&lt;br /&gt;Exception code: 0xe0434352&lt;br /&gt;Fault offset: 0x0000000000008e6c&lt;br /&gt;Faulting process id: 0x1554&lt;br /&gt;Faulting application start time: 0x01d4fb20fc5c3b3d&lt;br /&gt;Faulting application path: C:\\Program Files\\Veritas\\Backup Exec\\BackupExec.exe&lt;br /&gt;Faulting module path: C:\\Windows\\system32\\KERNELBASE.dll&lt;br /&gt;Report Id: 3a3f9d26-6714-11e9-80ee-005056053431&lt;br /&gt;Faulting package full name:&lt;br /&gt;Faulting package-relative application ID:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Application: BackupExec.exe&lt;br /&gt;Framework Version: v4.0.30319&lt;br /&gt;Description: The process was terminated due to an unhandled exception.&lt;br /&gt;Exception Info: System.Reflection.AmbiguousMatchException&lt;br /&gt;   at System.RuntimeType.GetMethodImpl(System.String, System.Reflection.BindingFlags, System.Reflection.Binder, System.Reflection.CallingConventions, System.Type[], System.Reflection.ParameterModifier[])&lt;br /&gt;   at System.Type.GetMethod(System.String, System.Reflection.BindingFlags)&lt;br /&gt;   at BackupExec.ThemeManager..cctor()&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Exception Info: System.TypeInitializationException&lt;br /&gt;   at BackupExec.ThemeManager.ChangeTheme(System.String, System.String)&lt;br /&gt;   at BackupExec.App..ctor()&lt;br /&gt;   at BackupExec.App.Main()&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;Cause&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;.NET Framework 4.8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=\"section-title\"&gt;Solution&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This issue has been addressed in BE 20.5, which is now available in the Download Center, please go to &lt;a href=\"http://support.veritas.com\"&gt;support.veritas.com&lt;/a&gt; to obtain this update.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Information regarding Backup Exec 16 will be provided at a later date.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Veritas recommends, where possible, to upgrade to the latest available version of Backup Exec. Upgrades can be found in the Downloads Center.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Temporary workaround:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Uninstall .NET Framework 4.8 and reboot server. This update will be listed as &lt;strong&gt;KB4486105 &lt;/strong&gt;(Windows 2012 R2), &lt;strong&gt;KB4486081&lt;/strong&gt; (Windows 2012), &lt;strong&gt;KB4486129&lt;/strong&gt; (Windows 2016), &lt;strong&gt;KB4486153&lt;/strong&gt; (Windows 2019) in the list of installed updates.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;ol start=\"2\"&gt;&lt;li&gt;For Windows 2008 R2, remove .NET Framework 4.8 through &lt;em&gt;Programs and Features&lt;/em&gt; in Control Panel.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: In case of Windows 2008 R2, re-install .NET Framework 4.x from Backup Exec install media (\\Veritas\\BE\\WinNT\\Install\\DotNetFx ) after uninstalling .NET Framework 4.8.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"section_RelatedArticles\" class=\"row\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 mb-5\"&gt;&lt;h2 id=\"title_RelatedArticles\"&gt;Related Knowledge Base Articles&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div id=\"data_RelatedArticles\" class=\"d-block\"&gt;&lt;div id=\"100046139\" class=\"article-link d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center w-100\"&gt;&lt;a class=\"d-block\" href=\"https://www.veritas.com/support/en_US/article.100046139.html\"&gt;.NET Framework 4.8 のインストール後、Backup Exec コンソールがクラッシュする&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"100010295\" class=\"article-link d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center w-100\"&gt;&lt;a class=\"d-block\" href=\"https://www.veritas.com/support/en_US/article.100010295.html\"&gt;Drive(s) appears in Microsoft Windows Disk Management. but does not appear in System Recovery Console&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=\"section_Reference\" class=\"row\"&gt;&lt;div class=\"col-12 mb-5\"&gt;&lt;h2 id=\"title_Reference\"&gt;References&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div id=\"data_Reference\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"d-block\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"font-weight-medium\"&gt;Etrack&lt;/span&gt; : 3978206&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"d-block\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"font-weight-medium\"&gt;SW_DOWNLOAD&lt;/span&gt; : UPD647494&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=\"d-block\"&gt;_______________________________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 0, 0),
