('2019-09-20 17:50:05', '2019-09-20 17:50:05', 1508, 6943, '2019-09-20 17:50:05', 64, '&lt;p&gt;Em contato com a ITS, foi informado que houve um rompimento de fibra e que por conta disso, nosso link foi colocado em um link de backup para n&atilde;o haver interrup&ccedil;&atilde;o. Este link backup tem a velocidade mais reduzida, o que provocou a lentid&atilde;o que sentimos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Verificamos o fortigate e identificamos consumos pontuais de youtube.&lt;br /&gt;Com orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o de Marcos Cruz, foi bloqueado o acesso ao Youtube dos grupos de navega&ccedil;&atilde;o:&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;GG_FIREWALL_PARCIAL2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;GG_FIREWALL_PARCIAL3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;GG_FIREWALL_PARCIAL4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Teste de velocidade com o link da Embratel&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1720&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; &gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;354c9a6d-4a789a11-5d853a4345ffd0.34118840&quot; width=&quot;474.00000000000006&quot; src=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1720&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1721&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; &gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;354c9a6d-4a789a11-5d853b2c870ec1.09991759&quot; width=&quot;474&quot; src=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1721&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At&eacute; restabelecer o servi&ccedil;o da ITS, o link foi desativado no fortigate.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Estamos atualmente com o link da Embratel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 0, 0),
('2019-09-21 08:22:33', '2019-09-21 08:22:33', 1509, 6943, '2019-09-21 08:22:33', 64, '&lt;p&gt;Link ITS Restabelecido.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1722&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; &gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;354c9a6d-4a789a11-5d8607088068e9.49587361&quot; width=&quot;597&quot; src=&quot;/tecnologia/front/document.send.php?docid=1722&amp;tickets_id=6943&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 0, 0);
